snippet.textDisplay: I really like Christina Aguilera as a vocalist and I hope she can come back with an amazing album where she can show off her vocal range and versatility as a singer. However, "Ave Maria" is not a song that you should "make your own" or do the runs she always does. Show some versatility as a singer and do the best version of this song possible, if anyone can do it, it's Christina Aguilera with that powerful voice. Part of being a great vocalist is being under control, showing restraint and going all out where it calls for that.
